text: Anna Henrietta Bergendahl (born December 11, 1991) in Katrineholm, Sweden is a singer. She was a contestant on Swedish Idol 2008. Bergendahl won Melodifestivalen 2010 and represented Sweden in the Eurovision Song Contest 2010 in Oslo.
